Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:07.76,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经拥有这世上一切的传说中的海贼王 哥鲁德·罗杰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.27,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在临死前的一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.50,0:00:12.33,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人们趋之若鹜奔向大海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:14.27,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子的财宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.59,0:00:16.05,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种的话 就去领吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:17.09,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:19.79,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把这世上的一切都放在了那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:22.42,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是人们启程追寻梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:25.19,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海贼时代来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.33,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想获得「ONE PIECE」的所有海贼都憧憬的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.74,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伟大航路后半段海域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:42.45,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:47.96,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 曾经征服过那片大海的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.21,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有海贼王哥鲁德·罗杰一人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:57.63,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新世界不断阻挡着众多海贼的梦想和野心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:03.74,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今在这片大海上 吃了橡皮果实并成了橡皮人的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:07.23,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙奇·D·路飞和他的伙伴们正向其发起挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.24,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海贼王!我当定了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.63,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在激战中获胜的草帽小子一伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:23.13,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于踏入了四皇所统治的世界最强之海新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:27.79,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一伙人因接到了紧急信号而踏上了「Punk Hazard」岛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:33.11,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是分为燃烧的土地与冰之土地的奇妙岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:36.53,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了解救被神秘集团绑架的娜美等人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:39.20,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路飞等人向冰之土地进发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:47.59,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一伙人此时还不知道与他们有缘之人也在这座岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:53.68,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到本人的别墅有何贵干 白猎人家的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:04:03.24,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,2000)}七武海!\N托拉法尔加·劳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:43.35,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托拉法尔加 就算你身为七武海我们也不能罢手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.00,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请从那里让开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:51.27,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经知道这座岛上还有其他人在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:58.75,Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,260)\fad(500,0)}原贝卡邦克博士的研究所内\N—  娜美方面  —
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:57.87,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:08.24,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们刚才说过病已经好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.64,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:15.08,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看起来并不像是病人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:16.40,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:19.38,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们说我们得了病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.39,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且要花费一年时间才能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:28.51,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年才能治好病?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:38.67,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们就被父母委托给我们治病的人带到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:42.17,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是父母让你们来这里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:46.97,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在家外边那些人突然对我们那么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.56,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就直接被带到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:52.78,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是病传染给父母就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.52,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连和他们告别的机会都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:56.73,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人也是一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.31,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:01.55,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议 这怎么看都像是绑架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:06.75,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能和父母告别就被陌生人带过来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:11.07,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那莫非是...非常严重的疾病吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.29,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:15.27,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑步感觉辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.57,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到累的人我来背
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.06,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来都很精神嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:23.77,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:26.25,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为主人给我们治疗过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:27.37,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.27,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:30.95,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:37.20,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 主人...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:44.21,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是说好的一年治疗期也已经过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:46.64,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔巴 等会儿给他们诊断一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:47.73,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诊断之后就会明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:49.80,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.96,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这扇门上锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.06,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:05.45,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人会追来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.16,0:07:07.17,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:08.46,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得抓紧才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:09.30,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.50,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.38,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:18.21,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:21.80,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:22.57,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗力变强了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:24.56,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅啊 小狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:27.64,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是狸猫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:29.40,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在真的好像狸猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:30.51,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.05,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.06,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:37.14,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔巴 把你的毛皮借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.79,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:40.39,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这能脱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:41.83,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是什么地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:42.92,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:44.40,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是冰柜?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.93,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太暗了什么都看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:50.04,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说这天气倒是刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.30,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冬岛长大的就是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.11,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里应该是路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.30,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太暗了实在是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.87,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了 里面还有扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:00.85,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:02.07,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接着走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:03.55,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是死路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:04.62,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:07.84,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 这里不行 好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:11.97,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:14.05,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧啊 追兵要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:17.68,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条路我们第一次来的时候走过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:18.69,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.03,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这里肯定是通向出口的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:24.99,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很冷 但是大家忍耐一下 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:25.95,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:29.40,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.22,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:43.81,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:49.98,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墙里好像有什么东西...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:09.26,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条路上有被冻住的人们 很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.07,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:14.01,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被冻住的尸体?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:16.97,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面也有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:19.70,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面也有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.48,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:27.73,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你们等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.49,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丢下我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:32.06,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:35.50,Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,260)\fad(500,0)}研究所内·饼干屋\N—  香吉方面  —
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.73,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路已经封住了 足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:39.96,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧吧 我刚才感觉到娜美小姐内心的呼唤了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.18,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是向我告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.78,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这些家伙到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:48.83,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下半身是羊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:51.90,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空想中倒是存在这种生物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.91,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去考虑这些家伙也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:57.28,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先彻底了解这里的全貌才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:09:59.81,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那些 现在更重要的是娜美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:01.07,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.59,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管在下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:03.63,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下要留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:06.97,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走的孩子们中并没有见到吾儿的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:08.79,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还有别的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:10.29,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下要留下来去找...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.66,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要怎么去找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:14.36,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你丢下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.98,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就跟见死不救没什么区别了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.91,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后想起来也不会好受的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:22.26,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在下是来救儿子的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.91,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个急人的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:27.30,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接拜托我们不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:29.15,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说一句帮我找找身体会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.53,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体到底在哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.64,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下绝不会欠海贼的人情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.57,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死也不会求你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:44.93,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但...但是如果你想帮忙找在下的身体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:48.14,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:51.93,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 区区一个人头还摆什么臭架子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.44,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想动粗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:55.39,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死...死而无憾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.93,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下绝不会向恶徒求饶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:10:59.48,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.95,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉一个手无寸铁的人头 你就能解气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:08.90,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他从那个房间带出来的那一刻起你就已经输了 香吉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.24,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.62,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死我啦 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:18.89,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一瞬间被他的觉悟打动的我真是个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.61,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经不想再帮他了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:27.87,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是想把手无缚鸡之力的在下带在身边也无妨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:36.20,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 等你身体复原有你好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:40.11,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真忍心对一个人头下手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:42.97,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你还是稍微注意点口气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.62,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜美他们应该找到出口了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.81,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼...好痒...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:45.55,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们追
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:47.65,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 好...好痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:56.27,Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,260)\fad(500,0)}Punk Hazard岛 中央之湖\N—  路飞方面  —
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:02.74,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把入侵者统统干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.59,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 被砍断了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:08.03,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:12.87,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一群无聊的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.33,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 索隆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:15.57,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表扬一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.52,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是足麻吕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.39,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把炮弹砍断了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:22.40,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋武士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:25.03,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要退缩 开火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:28.98,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误会还是没有解开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:31.87,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们怎么看都是一群脑袋秀逗的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.91,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 明明是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:35.65,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橡皮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.25,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「足麻吕气球」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.50,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:40.47,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足麻吕已经没有意义了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:45.57,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.90,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.15,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那副身体是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.12,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:54.94,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就好办了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:57.04,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.34,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还准备向这边开火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.06,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群不长记性的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.52,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:04.69,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:08.89,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在瞄准水面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:12.15,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想掀翻我们的小船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.53,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:16.24,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里可是有两个能力者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.36,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:21.29,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们所有人葬身海底
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.27,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.25,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:33.51,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:38.70,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:08.13,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先藏在冰块后面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.52,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.54,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强逃掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.91,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也稍微给我划一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.95,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海中能力者是没有战斗能力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:38.53,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉没吧 能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:44.07,Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,260)\fad(500,0)}研究所附近的雪山\N—  布鲁克方面  —
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:48.89,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心 太恶心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:52.01,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个妖怪到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:53.76,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就袭来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:58.15,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就没有理由被它袭击嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:14:59.90,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还非常强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.91,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像隐约听到了一些动静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:10.88,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我没有耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:17.41,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太难缠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:21.27,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 我只能应战了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.59,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就当做没看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:36.32,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我本来就没有眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:40.85,Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,295)\fad(500,0)}研究所 正面入口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:46.02,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂? 我叫蒙奇·D·路飞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:48.26,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要成为海贼王的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:49.98,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了 废话太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:52.83,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:53.85,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.80,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷...请问是老大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.20,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不是老大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:03.05,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙伴们一个个都被砍倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:06.22,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要被武士杀死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:07.28,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:10.45,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来都行 总之救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:14.45,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是「Punk Hazard」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:20.58,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛的名字 寒冷的气候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:26.27,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音的主人是从这座岛发出信号的没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:31.12,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识草帽小子路飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.97,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橡皮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:36.34,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「气球」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:37.77,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「反射」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:40.66,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ROOM」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:42.71,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「屠宰场」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:46.97,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:53.70,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前在肥皂泡群岛发生的天龙人罗兹沃德家的事件中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:57.14,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和基德以及草帽小子一同战斗过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.96,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更是在巅峰战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.60,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把草帽小子家交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:05.71,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带他从这里逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:07.97,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把他交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:14.67,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把被赤犬追击的草帽小子给放跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.32,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:27.42,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捏造紧急信号正是你们海军的拿手好戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:32.64,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 这通电话并不是我们所设下的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:34.43,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:36.73,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知情 谈话就到此结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:41.62,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少跟我来这套 让我进研究所看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.49,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是我的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:44.49,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕难从命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:49.11,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个海贼住在你们舍弃的岛上又有何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.48,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:55.75,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果草帽小子来这里的话 我会帮你们取下他的人头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:59.34,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其他事情就请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.18,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:17.21,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些被冻住的人们好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.93,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:21.81,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是快看 那里有门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.12,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能从这里出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:24.63,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.56,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面果然还是有人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:35.05,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:38.00,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.06,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从房子里出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:43.22,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以回家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:45.11,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能见到爸爸妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:45.65,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:46.75,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.52,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把道让开 小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.37,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福兰奇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:58.47,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是坦克哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:01.19,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我让道 给我让道 给我超级让道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:04.26,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事的家伙就一并碾碎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:07.72,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我会避开鲜花的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:11.79,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点小温柔的福兰奇坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:14.82,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我们上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:17.34,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:18.32,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:18.87,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:22.58,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:30.77,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草帽小子一伙? 孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:34.44,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经说不出来哪里奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:37.53,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大狸猫 严冬的比基尼 巨大的小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.22,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人 人头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.68,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在做梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.48,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,履带哇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:43.87,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.75,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害的坦克啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:47.13,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太究极了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:49.63,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路崎岖也是没有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:54.32,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜美小姐 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.30,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被冻僵的娜美小姐也好美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:20:00.07,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了就不好了 穿上我的上衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.75,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 香吉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:05.91,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认得你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.60,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 是在肥皂泡群岛遇到的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:12.52,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非把孩子们关起来的就是你 你这个人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:14.73,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会把孩子们还给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:17.06,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:20.80,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是哪里的恶棍呢 原来是斯摩格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:23.59,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那位可爱依旧的妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:26.02,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 想不到居然有海军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:28.61,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边不行 换一个出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:30.29,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家掉头回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.94,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 小鬼们 回里面去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.36,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会有后门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.86,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这种地方会有海军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.43,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊 总之先逃命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:45.59,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海军不是好人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.18,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 那就过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:50.08,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 那些人看起来都像流氓一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.58,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是还有别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.26,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么就一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:57.39,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:00.22,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也正吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:03.85,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 快去逮捕草帽小子一伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:08.29,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 大家上 跟着上校妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:10.23,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.57,0:21:11.37,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ROOM」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:18.71,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.36,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:28.15,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帮家伙尽给我添乱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.12,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「指挥棒」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:35.76,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:21:59.76,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:18.84,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军舰浮上天了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.26,0:22:21.16,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连河底都一起飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:23.64,Sub,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么情况啊
